{"tid":1799600,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TC Cander 2019 全球百大美女榜","createTime":"2019-12-27T05:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T13:30:21.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"949951a0f092974afd19ec029c6332c8343f9d3d","tid":1799600,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191227/photo/bkn-20191227111516422-1227_00862_001_01p.jpg?20191227121158\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191227111516422-1227_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20191227121158&h=353fa58a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國電影網站TC Candler每年年尾均會公布「全球百大美女排行榜」及「全球百大帥哥排行榜」，今年「百大美女榜」冠軍由土耳其女星Hande Ercel榮登榜首，力壓排在第2位的以色列超模Yael Shelbia。<br />\n<br />\n而韓國女團After School出身的NaNa今年再為韓國爭光，曾於2014年及2015年連續兩年獲得第一名的她，去年下跌至第6位，今年重登三甲，排名第3位，再次勇奪「亞洲第一美女」的美譽。"},{"pid":"2ff8c3836ea96ebc96729a60d93197b6e5763ba1","tid":1799600,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/77244208_2479898745672842_9019199035195451241_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_ohc=olrds38WA1EAX-hsjpX&amp;oh=814c9ee8def31dd205e5635dc52545d4&amp;oe=5EAD4836\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F77244208_2479898745672842_9019199035195451241_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_ohc%3Dolrds38WA1EAX-hsjpX%26oh%3D814c9ee8def31dd205e5635dc52545d4%26oe%3D5EAD4836&h=06ba57f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/75454126_1038128969871328_2959615239818444635_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ohc=NLH8UZi36J0AX-3R1Za&amp;oh=e9bd7a3c2a356948b4475c120435372e&amp;oe=