576729_1638464179629555_816818364892082184_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ohc%3Dxr5sXsF9FDsAX_Kj5A4%26oh%3Dda4628a00aeecbec7fce766b7d3872f2%26oe%3D5EAE02BE&h=4782836b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/79720338_877726869311058_5504677569751385846_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=eLVJzcGFwnYAX_JMFPy&amp;oh=ae8b09ca51d600c1bd174c4cfb5262a2&amp;oe=5EA7AA02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F79720338_877726869311058_5504677569751385846_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ohc%3DeLVJzcGFwnYAX_JMFPy%26oh%3Dae8b09ca51d600c1bd174c4cfb5262a2%26oe%3D5EA7AA02&h=e360989f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/75196166_158835198714565_8196846610420276184_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ohc=_eTx4Ii8jHQAX9cV0lo&amp;oh=4a531fd0c8085688dedbb32f5728ccf3&amp;oe=5EA3A5A8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F75196166_158835198714565_8196846610420276184_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ohc%3D_eTx4Ii8jHQAX9cV0lo%26oh%3D4a531fd0c8085688dedbb32f5728ccf3%26oe%3D5EA3A5A8&h=64e76e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於去年勇奪第2位的韓團TWICE台灣成員周子瑜，今年下跌至第15位。此外，今年入圍的韓國女星還包括第12位的韓團Red Velvet成員Irene，女團BLACK PINK成員Lisa與Jennie分別排第16及37位、失婚女星宋慧喬排第33位、Sandara排第46位、TWICE成員Sana排第50位、秀智則排在第54位。"},{"pid":"b8a72f29cd856f16ca4d34ba4f096313c985f0bc","tid":1799600,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"此外，美國模特兒Taylor Hill、泰國女星Urassaya Sperbund、英國女星「妙麗」愛瑪沃森（Emma Watson）及古巴演員Ana De Armas依次排在第4至第7位。內地女星迪麗熱巴與林允分別排名第8及20位。而「蜘蛛女」Zendaya與法國女模Thylane Blondeau亦分別進佔第9及10位。"},{"pid":"e901d2abbeb417d